{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.1","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 5:1","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.004.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.005.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Aux anciens<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-4: cf. Ac 20:28. 2 Co 4:2, 5. 1 Ti 3:1-7; 4:12.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.5.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Voici les exhortations que j\u2019adresse aux anciens qui sont parmi vous, moi ancien comme eux, t\u00e9moin des souffrances de Christ, et participant de la gloire qui doit \u00eatre manifest\u00e9e:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5","name":"1 Pierre 5","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5.2","name":"1 Pierre 5:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.4.19","name":"1 Pierre 4:19","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.4.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.2","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 5:2","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.005.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.005.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.5.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Paissez le troupeau de Dieu qui est sous votre garde, non par contrainte, mais volontairement, selon Dieu; non pour un gain sordide, mais avec d\u00e9vouement;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5","name":"1 Pierre 5","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5.3","name":"1 Pierre 5:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5.1","name":"1 Pierre 5:1","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.3","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 5:3","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.005.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.005.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.5.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>non comme dominant sur ceux qui vous sont \u00e9chus en partage, mais en \u00e9tant les mod\u00e8les du troupeau.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5","name":"1 Pierre 5","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5.4","name":"1 Pierre 5:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5.2","name":"1 Pierre 5:2","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.4","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 5:4","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.005.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.005.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.5.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Et lorsque le souverain pasteur para\u00eetra, vous obtiendrez la couronne incorruptible de la gloire.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5","name":"1 Pierre 5","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5.5","name":"1 Pierre 5:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5.3","name":"1 Pierre 5:3","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.5","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 5:5","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.005.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.005.006,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Humilit\u00e9 et vigilance<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 5-11: cf. (\u00c9p 5:21. Ph 2:3. Ja 4:6, 10.) (1 Th 5:6-8. \u00c9p 6:10-18.)<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.5.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>De m\u00eame, vous qui \u00eates jeunes, soyez soumis aux anciens. Et tous, dans vos rapports mutuels, rev\u00eatez-vous d\u2019humilit\u00e9; car Dieu r\u00e9siste aux orgueilleux, Mais il fait gr\u00e2ce aux humbles.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5","name":"1 Pierre 5","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5.6","name":"1 Pierre 5:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5.4","name":"1 Pierre 5:4","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.6","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 5:6","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.005.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.005.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.5.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Humiliez-vous donc sous la puissante main de Dieu, afin qu\u2019il vous \u00e9l\u00e8ve au temps convenable;<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5","name":"1 Pierre 5","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5.7","name":"1 Pierre 5:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5.5","name":"1 Pierre 5:5","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.7","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 5:7","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.005.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.005.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.5.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>et d\u00e9chargez-vous sur lui de tous vos soucis, car lui-m\u00eame prend soin de vous.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5","name":"1 Pierre 5","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5.8","name":"1 Pierre 5:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5.6","name":"1 Pierre 5:6","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.8","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 5:8","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.005.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.005.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.5.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Soyez sobres, veillez. Votre adversaire, le diable, r\u00f4de comme un lion rugissant, cherchant qui il d\u00e9vorera.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5","name":"1 Pierre 5","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5.9","name":"1 Pierre 5:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5.7","name":"1 Pierre 5:7","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.9","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 5:9","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.005.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.005.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.5.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>R\u00e9sistez-lui avec une foi ferme, sachant que les m\u00eames souffrances sont impos\u00e9es \u00e0 vos fr\u00e8res dans le monde.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5","name":"1 Pierre 5","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5.10","name":"1 Pierre 5:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5.8","name":"1 Pierre 5:8","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.10","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 5:10","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.005.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.005.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.5.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Le Dieu de toute gr\u00e2ce, qui vous a appel\u00e9s en J\u00e9sus-Christ \u00e0 sa gloire \u00e9ternelle, apr\u00e8s que vous aurez souffert un peu de temps, vous perfectionnera lui-m\u00eame, vous affermira, vous fortifiera, vous rendra in\u00e9branlables.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5","name":"1 Pierre 5","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5.11","name":"1 Pierre 5:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5.9","name":"1 Pierre 5:9","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.11","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 5:11","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.005.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.005.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.5.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>A lui soit la puissance aux si\u00e8cles des si\u00e8cles! Amen!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5","name":"1 Pierre 5","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5.12","name":"1 Pierre 5:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5.10","name":"1 Pierre 5:10","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.12","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 5:12","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.005.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.005.013,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">V\u0153ux et salutations<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 12-14: cf. 1 Th 5:23-28. 2 Co 13:12, 13.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.5.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>C\u2019est par Silvain, qui est \u00e0 mes yeux un fr\u00e8re fid\u00e8le, que je vous \u00e9cris ce peu de mots, pour vous exhorter et pour vous attester que la gr\u00e2ce de Dieu \u00e0 laquelle vous \u00eates attach\u00e9s est la v\u00e9ritable.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5","name":"1 Pierre 5","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5.13","name":"1 Pierre 5:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5.11","name":"1 Pierre 5:11","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.13","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 5:13","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.005.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"1Pet.005.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.5.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>L\u2019\u00c9glise des \u00e9lus qui est \u00e0 Babylone vous salue, ainsi que Marc, mon fils.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5","name":"1 Pierre 5","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5.14","name":"1 Pierre 5:14","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5.12","name":"1 Pierre 5:12","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.14","label":"","reference":"1 Pierre 5:14","prev_osis_id":"1Pet.005.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"2Pet.001.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"1Pet.5.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Saluez-vous les uns les autres par un baiser d\u2019affection. Que la paix soit avec vous tous qui \u00eates en Christ!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5","name":"1 Pierre 5","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:2Pet.1.1","name":"2 Pierre 1:1","id":"fra-LSG:2Pet.1.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:1Pet.5.13","name":"1 Pierre 5:13","id":"fra-LSG:1Pet.5.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fc033b963.51289121');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc033b963.51289121\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fc033b963.51289121","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fc033b963.51289121'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc033b963.51289121\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"